description: Erection of a part 7-storey, part 28-storey and part 30-storey building comprising hotel (Use Class C1) floorspace,residential (Use Class C3) floorspace and flexible retail and community floorspace (Use Class A1/D1), creation of a new 'left turn only' vehicular access from West India Dock Road, hard and soft landscape improvements to the adjacent areas of highway and public realm and other associated works.Minor Material Amendments to Planning permission Ref: PA/18/01203, Dated 27/03/2019:Amendments include: Overall increase of residential units from 66 to 68; Increase in affordable unit provision from 18 to 21; Amended residential unit mix; and Replacement of triplex penthouse units with duplex apartments.The application is accompanied by an Environmental Statement
site_name: 82 West India Dock Road, London, E14
